{
  "stem": "19055.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And two Jewish inmates came, picked up this old man-- [? we ?] was just beaten to death in front of me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They threw him up on the-- on the wagon, and-- and tooked him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was told afterwards-- I didn't know-- but I was told it was Ilsa Koch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] We did not go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All we did is just counting in the morning, Zahlappell and hanging around, and waiting, waiting--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--for our destiny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know why, but many, many people already died, because we ate the same food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I learned later that Bergen-Belsen was really a starvation camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans had experiments also, on minimizing calories, and how much a person can survive on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was the minimum calorie, and it was obviously-- was not enough for us there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a doctor in our barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish doctors were distributed in-- in different barracks, but they practically had nothing to treat us with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had aspirin, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there wouldn't-- no effort from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could not understand it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I cannot understand it, because the Germans were so afraid of diseases, that I-- I can't remember any-- any effort or-- or any-- any cleaning, even, facilities to-- to get rid of your clothing or changing.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In one of these-- Again, I-- I encounter somebody-- it-- it-- somehow, my good angels who-- who looked after us always provided with some good people along the line.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- We were having these zahlappell in the morning, and there was an old German sergeant, a-- an SS sergeant, had big, bushy eyebrows and the Nazi hat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had a pipe, always a pipe, so we called him Popeye.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
